{"parse":{"title":"Barbed Gill Trout","pageid":112008,"wikitext":{"*":"<onlyinclude>{{{{{tpl|tooltip}}}\n|mode={{{mode|}}}\n|arg={{{arg|}}}\n|sell={{cost|||8}}\n|icon=INV_Misc_Fish_37\n|quality=Common\n|itemid=27422\n|ilvl=60\n|name=Barbed Gill Trout}}</onlyinclude>\n\n==Source==\nThis is the most common [[fishing|fish]] in the [[Burning Crusade]]. It can be fished from all the lakes of [[Outland]]. It can also be fished from [[Deadwind Pass]], in the [[Eastern Kingdoms]].\n\n==Barbed Gill Trout as an ingredient==\nThis item is used to make: \n* {{loot|Common|Blackened Trout}}\n* {{loot|Common|Stewed Trout}}\n\n==External links==\n<!-- Read http://www.wowwiki.com/WoWWiki:External_links before posting your links here.\nLinks that do not conform to the rules will be DELETED.\nRepeat violations may result in a BAN.\nHave a nice day. :) -->\n{{elinks-item|27422}}\n{{Elink|link=http://www.elsanglin.com/fish/barbed_gill_trout.html |site=El's Extreme Anglin' |icon=elsanglin}}\n\n[[Category:World of Warcraft common items]]"}}}